HEADWORD: Stuffy
<hw>Stuff"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Stout;
mettlesome; resolute.</def> <mark>[Scot.]</mark>
<rj><au>Jamieson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Angry and obstinate; sulky.</def> <mark>[U.
S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Ill-ventilated; close.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

